  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: a1c44d26bee7f894782729c6bcff2b73, type: 3}
  m_Name: Chilli Conversation 2
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  SpeakerName: Yukio
  paragraphs:
  - 'DAYUM I FEEL INCREDIBLE


    You are the most amazing chef'
  - Only the best for my best friend
  - Pheww I feel so good I am on fire
  - "Okay Isagi, tell me about your night. \n\nDid you do what I asked?"
  - 'Oooh yes okay I have been looking forward to this.  '
  - But yes of course I did because I am the bestest in the whole world at what i
    do
  - I got in contact with Kenji - the detective you remember?
  - Of course
  - Right, well this guy was really strange but he agreed without hesitation
  - At this point so many detectives have turned us down this guy could be anyone
    and I would hire him
  - "Thank god, and I agree, I have waited too long already. \n\n"
  - I miss him.
  - Its okay Yukio, I am always here for you
  - "\u2026"
  - Except for right now, I got things (and the girl from last night) to do
  - Right, have fun with that
  - "Bye! and next time I WANT THE SAME THING\n\nIt feels illegal to feel this good\u2026"
